OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Mostly clear overnight, with a
OL,8,Fchance of frost in rural parts, as
OL,9,Fwinds fall generally light. Patchy
OL,10,Fhill fog may form over some high
OL,11,Fground into the early hours of
OL,12,FWednesday.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA dry day with long sunny
OL,15,Fspells and a brisk easterly breeze
OL,16,Fdeveloping, this perhaps becoming
OL,17,Fstrong over hills. Warm inland but
OL,18,Fcooler along coasts and over hills.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
